## Provenance fields

If the contract carries provenance (typical for hot-path dataclasses):

- `as_of_ns`: nanosecond timestamp of the input that produced this.
- `source_tick_seq`: monotonic sequence id from the originating tick.
- `model_name`: string identifier of the producing model.
- `params_version`: version tag for the calibration parameters used.

