## Tests required

These tests must exist and pass before any honouring action is
verified-complete:

- `tests/test_<contract_name>_shape.py` — assert the dataclass / sig
  exists with the named fields and types.
- `tests/test_<contract_name>_invariants.py` — assert invariants hold
  on a fixture instance.
- `tests/test_<contract_name>_raise.py` — assert each documented
  raise condition triggers the documented exception.

